name: Art Gallery Style
promptFragment: Sophisticated gallery aesthetic featuring crisp white walls as pristine backdrops. Directional track lighting or sleek wall sconces create dramatic visual focus. Minimal furniture ensures clean sightlines. Refined, elegant atmosphere with intense focus on visual impact and artistic presentation.

name: Biophilic Design (Green Office)
promptFragment: Nature-integrated design featuring lush living green walls and abundant potted plants. Natural materials like light-toned wood, cork, and stone paired with organic, curved furniture forms. Maximized natural light creates a serene, rejuvenating atmosphere fostering connection with the natural world.

name: Bohemian (Boho)
promptFragment: Free-spirited Bohemian aesthetic with an eclectic mix of patterns and rich textures. Warm earth tones like terracotta, rust, and sage green complemented by natural materials such as rattan, wicker, and bamboo. Inviting and serene atmosphere enhanced by abundant indoor plants, soft layered textiles, and warm, diffused lighting.

name: Boho Creative
promptFragment: Bohemian Creative aesthetic blending vintage and mid-century elements with an eclectic, personal touch. Warm natural wood surfaces layered with rich textures from patterned rugs and vibrant textiles. Curated gallery wall arrangements and soft, diffused lighting enhance a lived-in, inspiring atmosphere, complemented by abundant hanging and potted plants.

name: Botanical Conservatory
promptFragment: Lush botanical conservatory aesthetic filled with abundant greenery—large potted plants, hanging ferns, and trailing vines. Natural flooring materials like terracotta or slate. Vintage metal or weathered wood furniture creates an established, greenhouse atmosphere with verdant, garden-like tranquility.

name: Boutique Luxury (The "Dream Closet")
promptFragment: High-end boutique luxury aesthetic resembling an upscale fashion retail environment. Glass-fronted display cabinetry with integrated LED lighting. Premium finishes like marble and white lacquer surfaces. Statement chandelier or decorative lighting. Sophisticated, curated presentation with elegant organizational systems.

name: B&W Pencil Sketch
promptFragment: Hand-drawn black and white graphite pencil sketch on clean white paper background. Rough, expressive artistic lines with delicate shading and deliberate hatching techniques. Focus on form and spatial relationships rather than literal color or material detail. Preliminary yet sophisticated architectural concept aesthetic.

name: Classic Blueprint
promptFragment: Classic architectural blueprint style with deep rich blue background and crisp, clean white lines for all structural elements. Strict technical drawing aesthetic with high contrast and schematic precision. Professional drafting presentation.

name: Classic Pub | Billiard Room
promptFragment: Classic pub and gentlemans club aesthetic with rich, dark wood wainscoting and paneling. Leather seating with brass nail-head trim. Vintage-style pendant and sconce lighting. Warm, masculine, and sophisticated club-like atmosphere with traditional craftsmanship details.

name: Classic Wainscoting
promptFragment: Classic architectural wainscoting with molding—beadboard, board-and-batten, or chair rails—on lower wall sections. Contrasting soft colors or wallpaper above the rail. Classic wall sconces for elegant lighting. Traditional, refined character with timeless millwork details.

name: Clay Model (Monochrome)
promptFragment: Clean white clay model architectural visualization. Monochromatic white palette with soft ambient occlusion shadows highlighting form and geometry. No material textures or colors—pure focus on light, massing, and spatial relationships.

name: Clean & Bright (Minimalist Utility)
promptFragment: Clean and bright minimalist aesthetic emphasizing hygiene and freshness. All-white or very light palette with flat-panel cabinetry and light stone surfaces. Seamlessly integrated fixtures and appliances. Bright, cool lighting creating a pristine, organized atmosphere.

name: Clean Vector Line Art
promptFragment: Professional vector-style line drawing with clean, straightened lines and corrected perspective. Uniform black line weights on pure white background. Focus on clarity, geometric precision, and architectural accuracy. Technical illustration aesthetic.

name: Coastal | Hamptons
promptFragment: Coastal Hamptons aesthetic featuring crisp whites and soft blues. High-quality wicker or rattan furniture with comfortable cushions. Beadboard architectural details and natural fiber textiles (jute/sisal). Airy, breezy, and sophisticated beach-house elegance.

name: Corporate Professional
promptFragment: Corporate professional aesthetic prioritizing privacy and acoustics. Glass partitions maintain light flow while defining areas. High-quality commercial carpeting dampens sound. Neutral, professional color palette (greys, blues, beiges) conveying stability and professionalism. Clean, organized, business-appropriate atmosphere.

name: Cozy Bistro
promptFragment: Cozy bistro aesthetic with space-saving furniture like foldable metal bistro sets. Wood deck tiles or outdoor rugs over hard surfaces. Vertical greenery with railing planters and hanging pots. Intimate, charming European cafe atmosphere with efficient use of space.

name: Cozy Reading Nook
promptFragment: Cozy reading nook aesthetic with custom built-in shelving and comfortable seating like window seats or daybeds. Layered soft pillows and blankets in rich textures. Intimate, quiet hideaway atmosphere perfect for relaxation. Warm, enveloping comfort with soft ambient lighting.

name: Craftsman
promptFragment: Craftsman architectural aesthetic featuring thick, tapered columns often on stone piers. Mix of siding and shingles in earth tones (greens, blues, browns). Exposed roof rafters and wide eaves as architectural details. Handcrafted character with natural materials and honest construction.

name: Creative Huddle Space
promptFragment: Creative collaborative aesthetic with informal seating like lounges, bean bags, or high-top stools. Functional walls with floor-to-ceiling whiteboards or glass writing surfaces. Vibrant colors stimulating energy and brainstorming. Dynamic, flexible, and innovation-focused atmosphere.

name: Digital Concept Art
promptFragment: Polished digital concept art painting style with soft edges and dramatic lighting. Painterly aesthetic focusing on atmosphere, mood, and color harmony rather than strict photorealism. Production art quality suitable for film or game visualization.

name: Executive Library (Traditional)
promptFragment: Executive library aesthetic with rich, dark wood tones (walnut or mahogany) for furniture and built-in shelving. Substantial leather seating (tufted or high-back). Scholarly, authoritative, and timeless atmosphere. Traditional craftsmanship with warm ambient lighting.

name: Grand Traditional (First Impression)
promptFragment: Grand traditional aesthetic focusing on symmetry and elegance. Premium flooring like marble (checkered or bordered patterns). Curated furniture arrangements with statement pieces. Large mirrors and statement chandeliers. Impressive, welcoming atmosphere with classical proportions.

name: High-End Photorealism
promptFragment: High-end photorealistic 3D rendering with physically based rendering (PBR) materials on all surfaces. Warm, natural sunlight creating realistic shadows. Plush, high-quality furniture and finishes. Professional architectural visualization quality.

name: Industrial Chef's Kitchen
promptFragment: Industrial chef aesthetic prioritizing functionality with commercial-grade stainless steel surfaces and appliances. Open metal shelving instead of closed cabinetry. Exposed architectural details like brick or ductwork. Subway tile and concrete finishes. Professional, utilitarian atmosphere.

name: Industrial Loft
promptFragment: Industrial loft aesthetic incorporating raw materials like exposed brick walls, concrete floors, and visible ductwork. Black metal finishes and distressed leather furniture. Masculine, edgy, and spacious warehouse atmosphere with high ceilings and open layouts.

name: Industrial Man Cave
promptFragment: Industrial man cave aesthetic embracing raw construction elements like concrete floors and exposed ceiling beams. Neon signage and entertainment features. Sturdy metal and wood furniture. Bold, masculine atmosphere perfect for socializing and entertainment.

name: Ink & Marker Sketch
promptFragment: Hand-drawn architectural concept sketch aesthetic with strong black ink outlines for geometry. Alcohol marker style coloring for surfaces and furniture. Loose, expressive lines suggesting a creative design phase. Artistic, conceptual presentation.

name: Ink & Watercolor
promptFragment: Professional ink and watercolor illustration aesthetic with distinct black ink outlines defining structure. Soft, translucent watercolor washes in vibrant but natural colors. Artistic, hand-crafted character maintaining sketch authenticity.

name: Japandi (Zen Sanctuary)
promptFragment: Japandi aesthetic blending Scandinavian functionality with Japanese rustic minimalism. Low-profile furniture and natural materials like bamboo, light wood, and linen. Warm neutral colors (cream, beige, stone). Zen, uncluttered sanctuary atmosphere with mindful simplicity.

name: Jungle Adventure
promptFragment: Jungle adventure theme with deep greens and earthy browns. Botanical or animal-themed patterns and wallpaper. Adventurous elements like canvas textures, wooden accents, and nature-inspired decor. Wild but cozy hideout atmosphere with exploratory character.

name: Luxury Fitness Club (Equinox Style)
promptFragment: Luxury fitness club aesthetic with dark, moody color palette (charcoal, black, dark wood). Full-wall mirrors expanding space. Architectural lighting (LED strips, recessed fixtures). Sleek, high-end black finishes. Exclusive, premium atmosphere.

name: Luxury Glamour (Marble)
promptFragment: Luxury glamour aesthetic with floor-to-ceiling marble or porcelain (Calacatta or Carrara style). Brushed gold or brass fixtures and hardware. Elegant lighting features. High-end, 5-star hotel suite atmosphere with opulent finishes.

name: Mid-Century Modern
promptFragment: Mid-century modern aesthetic with low-pitched or flat roof lines and wide, overhanging eaves. Clerestory windows and material palette of brick, wood, and glass. Pops of accent color (orange or teal). Clean geometric forms with organic influences.

name: Mid-Century Style Dining
promptFragment: Mid-century modern aesthetic with walnut or teak furniture featuring tapered legs. Iconic chair designs like Wishbone or molded shell silhouettes. Statement lighting (sputnik or globe style). Retro-chic, sophisticated atmosphere with timeless design.

name: Minimalist Boutique
promptFragment: Minimalist boutique aesthetic treating items like art in a gallery. Stark, clean backgrounds with white walls and concrete floors. Minimal shelving and displays avoiding overcrowding. Dramatic spotlighting highlighting focal points. Curated, gallery-like presentation.

name: Modern Contemporary
promptFragment: Modern contemporary aesthetic with geometric box-like forms and flat roof lines. Mixed materials like cedar wood siding, smooth concrete, and matte black metal. Large floor-to-ceiling windows connecting indoor and outdoor spaces. Clean, bold architectural expression.

name: Modern Family Rec Room
promptFragment: Modern family aesthetic prioritizing versatility for all ages. Durable, comfortable furniture like large sectionals. Plenty of built-in storage solutions. Bright, neutral, and inviting color palette. Practical, welcoming atmosphere for gathering and activities.

name: Modern Farmhouse
promptFragment: Modern farmhouse aesthetic with substantial, rustic wooden furniture. Black timber accents (Windsor style elements) and natural wood finishes. Iron linear or lantern-style lighting. Bright walls (white or cream) with optional shiplap texture. Warm, contemporary rustic character.

name: Modern Functional (Mudroom Hybrid)
promptFragment: Modern functional aesthetic prioritizing organization. Built-in seating with integrated storage. Wall hooks or sleek coat racks. Clean, simple lines with large mirrors. Durable flooring materials. Practical, streamlined, highly organized atmosphere.

name: Modern Infinity
promptFragment: Modern infinity aesthetic with water features appearing flush with surroundings (knife-edge or perimeter overflow) for mirror-like effects. Light-colored stone coping (limestone or travertine). Uncluttered surroundings with sleek, modern furnishings. Seamless, luxurious atmosphere.

name: Modern Lounge
promptFragment: Modern lounge aesthetic as seamless extension of contemporary design. Sleek, low-profile furniture that doesnt obstruct views. Black-framed elements and polished concrete or light wood flooring. Minimal decor focusing on openness and connection to surroundings.

name: Modern Marketing Plan (2D)
promptFragment: Clean, modern 2D floor plan aesthetic with flat colors and vector-like lines. Walls rendered in solid grey or black. Color-coded flooring (light wood tones, tile patterns) kept flat without 3D shadows. Focus on clarity and readability for professional presentation.

name: Modern Minimalist
promptFragment: Modern minimalist aesthetic with clean lines, open space, and monochromatic color palette (whites, greys, blacks). Functional furniture with simple geometric shapes. Clutter-free and ornamentation-free. Maximized natural light. Pure, refined simplicity.

name: Modern Oasis (Concrete & Fire)
promptFragment: Modern oasis aesthetic with large-format concrete pavers and grass or gravel grout lines. Sleek, rectangular fire features as focal points. Modern, weather-resistant furnishings. Structural, minimal landscaping. Contemporary outdoor luxury.

name: Modern Real Estate Staging (Neutral)
promptFragment: Modern transitional staging aesthetic with neutral color palette (beiges, greys, whites) appealing to wide audiences. Perfectly scaled furniture showing potential without cluttering. Bright, inviting lighting. Professional, aspirational presentation.

name: Modern Spa (Zen/Japandi)
promptFragment: Modern spa sanctuary aesthetic with natural materials like teak wood, slate, and river stone. Freestanding soaking elements as focal points. Soft, warm ambient lighting with greenery accents. Calming, Zen-like atmosphere promoting relaxation and wellness.

name: Montessori Minimalist
promptFragment: Montessori minimalist aesthetic where everything is accessible and child-scaled. Low furniture and open shelving at reachable heights. Spacious, uncluttered layouts fostering independence and focus. Neutral, calming colors with educational organization.

name: Moody & Bold (Patterned)
promptFragment: Moody and bold aesthetic with deep, rich colors like navy blue, forest green, or charcoal. Statement flooring with bold, patterned encaustic or geometric tiles. Metallic accents (brass or gold) adding luxury. Dramatic, sophisticated atmosphere.

name: Photorealistic Rendering (Sketch-to-Reality)
promptFragment: Photorealistic interpretation transforming rough sketches into high-quality realistic images. Realistic details, textures, and lighting filling in conceptual gaps. Sketched outlines become real objects with authentic materials. Professional visualization quality.

name: Realistic 3D (Orthographic)
promptFragment: High-quality photorealistic 3D floor plan rendering with orthographic top-down view. Realistic textures (wood flooring, tiles), soft global illumination shadows, and ambient occlusion showing depth. Modern furniture proportionally scaled. Professional architectural presentation.

name: Restoration / Declutter
promptFragment: General restoration and declutter aesthetic removing mess and wear-and-tear. Repaired surfaces (walls, floors) made fresh and clean. Bright, natural lighting enhancement. Existing style preserved while making space look new, maintained, and pristine.

name: Retro Arcade (80s)
promptFragment: Retro 1980s arcade aesthetic with bold patterns like checkered surfaces or neon-printed textures. Vintage arcade cabinet and pinball machine styling. Vibrant, colorful lighting creating nostalgic, energetic mood. Fun, playful atmosphere with retro gaming character.

name: Rustic Beam Cabin
promptFragment: Rustic cabin retreat aesthetic highlighting heavy exposed wooden beams. Warm wood paneling on ceilings or walls. Cozy, hearty textiles like wool and plaid patterns. Warm, enclosed, and safe atmosphere with mountain lodge character.

name: Rustic Outdoor Living (Pergola)
promptFragment: Rustic outdoor living aesthetic with wooden pergola structures providing shade and definition. Natural flagstone surfaces. Stone features like fireplaces or pizza ovens. Large, sturdy wooden furniture. Natural, established outdoor character.

name: Scandi (Scandinavian)
promptFragment: Scandinavian design aesthetic with light-colored woods (ash or pine), soft neutral colors, and cozy textures (wool, linen). Functionality and hygge atmosphere prioritized. Botanical accents and simple, elegant furniture. Warm, inviting Nordic character.

name: Spanish / Mediterranean
promptFragment: Spanish Mediterranean aesthetic with warm white or cream stucco textures. Red terracotta barrel tile roofing. Arched architectural elements, wrought iron details, and decorative tile work. Warm, sun-drenched character with Old World charm.

name: Tech Startup (Open Plan)
promptFragment: Modern tech startup aesthetic with open-plan layouts and shared work surfaces. Industrial elements like polished concrete floors and exposed ceilings. Acoustic baffles or clouds overhead. Pops of vibrant color and collaborative breakout zones. Energetic, innovative atmosphere.

name: Traditional Elegant (Runner)
promptFragment: Traditional elegant aesthetic contrasting dark wood with crisp white painted elements. Patterned carpet runners secured with metallic stair rods (brass or nickel). Classic turned spindles and balusters. Timeless, refined character with careful craftsmanship.

name: Tropical Lagoon
promptFragment: Tropical lagoon aesthetic with freeform, organic shapes rather than geometric forms. Natural boulders and waterfall features. Darker finishes creating deep, ocean-like appearances. Dense tropical landscaping. Exotic, resort-like paradise atmosphere.

name: Urban Lounge
promptFragment: Urban rooftop lounge aesthetic focusing on views with seamless glass railings. Social zones with sectional seating and fire features. Ambient lighting (string lights, lanterns) for evening atmosphere. Bar and entertaining areas. Sophisticated urban outdoor living.

name: Vintage Traditional
promptFragment: Vintage traditional aesthetic with classic elements like clawfoot fixtures, pedestal forms, and wainscoting on lower walls. Black and white patterned floor tiles. Chrome cross-handle hardware completing the timeless look. Nostalgic, elegant character.

name: Watercolor Illustration
promptFragment: Artistic watercolor architectural illustration style with white paper texture background. Soft edges, pastel color washes, and hand-painted aesthetic. Landscape and plants highlighted with soft greens, living areas with warm tones. Artistic, conceptual presentation.

name: Whimsical Fairytale
promptFragment: Whimsical fairytale aesthetic with soft pastel color palette (blush pinks, powder blues, lavenders). Magical elements like wall murals (clouds, forests), canopy structures, and house-frame furniture. Soft accent lighting like fairy lights creating dreamy, enchanted vibe.

name: Wireframe Tech (Holographic)
promptFragment: Technical wireframe rendering aesthetic with dark background. All edges and furniture outlined in glowing blue or white lines simulating CAD software or holographic projection. Structure emphasized over texture. Futuristic, digital visualization.

name: Xeriscaping (Desert Modern)
promptFragment: Xeriscape desert modern aesthetic replacing water-hungry elements with decorative gravel or decomposed granite. Drought-tolerant species like agave, yucca, and succulents. Corten steel or concrete planters for architectural structure. Sustainable, sculptural landscape design.

name: Zen Garden (Japanese)
promptFragment: Japanese zen garden aesthetic with elements like raked sand or gravel representing water. Deliberately placed large, mossy rocks. Japanese maples, bamboo, and shaped evergreens. Asymmetry, balance, and tranquility. Meditative, contemplative atmosphere.
